{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"242","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"研究：暖化升溫3.2°C 亞馬遜50%物種逃不過滅絕","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>研究發現，按照本世紀末預測，也就是暖化升溫3.2&deg;C的情境下，可能導致亞馬遜流失幾乎50％的動物物種。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>研究人員檢視在全球35個自然生態最豐富地區，氣候變遷對近8萬種植物和動物的影響，發現若不積極因應氣候變遷，亞馬遜、加拉巴戈群島、馬達加斯加以及歐洲海岸和加勒比海等世界上生物多樣性最豐富的地區，超過一半的野生動植物，可能因溫度上升而在本世紀末面臨滅絕。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/0411.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 389px;' /><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);'>非洲象（</span><em style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);'>Loxodonta africana</em><span style='color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);'>）每天需要喝150至300升的水，氣候變遷可能衝擊牠們的水源供給。圖片來源：WWF</span></p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>由世界野生動植物基金會（WWF）、東英吉利大學和詹姆斯庫克大學合作的<a href='https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s10584-018-2158-6' style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; color: rgb(95, 151, 8); text-decoration-line: none;' target='_blank'>研究</a>，探討了三種不同的氣候變遷情境：全球氣溫上升2&deg;C&mdash;&mdash;即巴黎氣候協定中規定的上限、上升3.2&deg;C&mdash;&mdash;即本世紀末升溫預測、上升4.5&deg;C&mdash;&mdash;碳排放持續上升的結果。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>結果顯示，全球平均氣溫升高4.5&deg;C將對植物和動物造成毀滅性影響，亞馬遜面臨植物物種減少69％的風險。3.2&deg;C的升溫可能導致亞馬遜流失幾乎50％的動物物種。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>在以生物多樣性聞名的島國馬達加斯加，大約60％的物種瀕臨滅絕 ，在非洲南部的米揚博林地，則有高達80％的哺乳動物瀕臨滅絕。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>研究警告，氣候變遷導致平均氣溫升高和天氣不穩定等現象，也會衝擊動植物生態，地中海、馬達加斯加和阿根廷塞拉多&mdash;潘塔納爾的降雨量會明顯減少。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>這可能影響非洲象的水源供給，這些大象需要每天喝大約150-300升水。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>不斷上升的海平面，將淹沒印度和孟加拉海岸線上的世界最大蘇達班紅樹林，當地是重要的老虎繁殖地。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>主要研究者、UEA廷德爾氣候變化研究中心華倫（Rachel Warren）教授表示：「我們的研究量化了限制暖化在2&deg;C對全球35個生物多樣性熱點的好處。」</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>「我們研究了8萬種植物、哺乳動物、鳥類、爬蟲和兩棲動物發現，如果沒有氣候政策，50％的物種可能會從這些地區流失。但是如果全球暖化可限制在工業化前以上2&deg;C內，這個比例可降至25％。」</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>「我們沒有研究將升溫限制在1.5&deg;C以內會怎麼樣，但預期可以保護更多的野生動物。」</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>資料來源:http://e-info.org.tw/node/210727</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2018-04-11","clk_count":"150"}},"__N_SSG":true}